chwirkt und theoretisch herausfordert.Am Beispiel wegweisender Arbeiten speziell aus der Spätphase (Shakespeare, Gorki, Cechov, Schimmelpfennig), analysiert Stefan Tigges autorenspezifische sowie autorenübergreifende künstlerische Suchbewegungen und signifikante Entwicklungsschritte von Jürgen Gosch und Johannes Schütz.  aStefan Tigges analyzes movements of artistic search as well as significant developmental steps of German theater director Jürgen Gosch and scenic designer Johannes Schütz on the basis of groundbreaking works especially from the late phase (Shakespeare, Gorki, Þ-U+010C-Þechov, Schimmelpfennig).  afunded by Deutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 4aBühnenbild. 4aJohannes Schütz. 4aJürgen Gosch. 4aRegie. 4aTheatergeschichte. 4aTheaterwissenschaft. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Theater / History & Criticism.2bisacsh  aDirection.  aHistory of Theatre.  aJohannes Schütz.  aJürgen Gosch.  aSet.  aTheatre Studies.1 aHarzer, Jens.2 aDeutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2021z9783110753790oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://doi.org/10.14361/9783839445952zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839445952423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783839445952.jpg  a978-3-11-074335-7  DG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2b2021  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2021  aZDB-23-DPKb2021